replies.body:
{{champion:161}} 
He has CC, has poke, all in burst, doesn't fall off, good waveclear, can use Q or ult to help other lanes from where the enemies can't see you (tribush or river bush), huge teamfight damage, and can even kite with his low cooldowns. He can also cs from a long range with mana refund on Q if he gets behind.

Only disadvantage I see is he's squishy and immobile like almost all mages
